  "description": "<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">暑期又到了，各位骚年有何打算？</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">死宅？可以有！旅游？也可以有！暑假年年有，今年有没有胆量一起</span><strong><span style=\"color: #EE33EE; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">逆袭</span></strong><span style=\"color: #EE33EE; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\"><strong>GRE</strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: #EE33EE; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">词汇</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">？！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">GRE</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">全称</span><span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">Graduate Record Examination</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">, </span></span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">戏称</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\"><strong>God Reading English</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">。这也就难怪</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">GRE </span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">考试总是弄得天怒人怨、人神共愤！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">但是，真的就没有办法搞定么？真的么？真的么？（</span><em><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">自带回音</span></em><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\"><em>N</em></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">多遍......</span></em><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">鲁迅先生说过：世上本没有路，走的人多了，也便成了路</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">阿基米德说：给我一个支点，我可以撬动地球</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">奥巴马说：</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\"> <strong>Yes, I &nbsp;can</strong><strong> !</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">&nbsp;GRE </span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">虽然难，但是只要我们步步为营，一定可以攻破。首先就从</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">GRE</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">词汇入手！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">说到</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">GRE</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">词汇，可谓是单词巅峰。有多少人被折磨的死去活来、捶胸顿足、仰天长啸！又有多少人几番轮回过来仍然只能清晰记得</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\"><strong>abandon</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">。其实如果方法得当，就算一个</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\"><strong>abandon</strong></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">也能学到彩头！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"color: #337FE5; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">求破！</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">两条路线！</span><strong><span style=\"color: #E56600; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">内线攻心</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">!</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">很多同学背单词只不过记住了形态，但是如果来一回庖丁解牛，各位的记忆一定会加深！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">为什么</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">abandon </span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">解释为抛弃、放纵？</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">a-</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">（</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">to</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">）</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">+bandon</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">（</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">power</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">）&rarr;愿意服务于某项权利而放弃自己的利益&rarr;放纵、抛弃</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">Only weak and cowardly natures</span><b><u><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\"> abandon themselves to</span></u></b><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\"> sorrow.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">只有那些软弱怯懦之人才会让自己沉浸在悲伤之中（</span><em><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">有志青年决不能如此！握拳！</span></em><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">）</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">abandon oneself to</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">: </span></span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">陷入、沉浸于</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">&hellip;..</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">中</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"color: #E56600; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">外线扩展战果</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">！一次只能记住一个词？效率真心不够！因此外线作战的时候注意尽量扩大内容。比如</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">abandon oneself to</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">的含义可以换其他单词来表达</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">:</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">（</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">）</span><b><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">indulge</span></b><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\"> <b>in</b></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">We all like to </span><b><u><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">indulge in</span></u></b><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\"> a bit of fantasy.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">（2）</span><b><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">surrender oneself to</span></b></p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">We </span><b><u><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">surrender ourselves</span></u></b><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\"> easily</span><b> <u><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">to</span></u> </b><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">pleasure.</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">而indulge 和surrender 两个词还有很多内容值得学习，这里就不做赘述了。。这样一来，通过最普通的abandon,我们可以</span><strong><span style=\"color: #E53333; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">学到什么</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">呢？</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">abandon</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">&rarr;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">abandon oneself to</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">&rarr;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">indulge in</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">&rarr;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">indulge</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">&rarr;</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">&hellip;&hellip;..(</span><em><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">to be continued</span></em><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">)</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">surrender oneself to</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">&rarr;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">surrender</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">&rarr;</span><span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">&hellip;&hellip;.. (</span><em><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">to be continued</span></em><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">)</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">通过这样内外交织的方法，可以达到</span><strong><span style=\"color: #E53333; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">两个效果</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">：</span><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">第一</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">，</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">通过词根词缀的方法可以更深刻的认知单词</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">；从而进一步对单词的记忆程度、使用方法有所裨益。第二，通</span><strong><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">过派生的方法尽可能多的获取与主单词相关的近反义词</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">。这种方法对之后做填空题有很大的帮助。一轮下来词汇量和对不同义项进行辨析的能力也会大有提高。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">怎么样，只要有正确适用的方法，</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">GRE</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">词汇需要考察的内容也一样可以拿下。不过最后提示各位有志于</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">GRE</span><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">词汇的同学，词汇是一定要力气去记的。但是咱们得使巧力，快准狠的抓住重点！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"color: #EE33EE; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei';\">只要你有决心学习，有信心挑战，都可以逆袭</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: Microsoft YaHei;\">！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://i1.s.hjfile.cn/entry/201307/69b0848b-6a03-4e65-b5f6-0b667dfbf351.gif\" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong> &nbsp;</strong></span><a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/132862/intro?source=880\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">新</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">GRE</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">核心词汇班</span></strong></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span><a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/coupon/2047?source=0\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>优惠劵</strong></span></a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p499713/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p499713\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p498900/\">外媒关注中国屌丝：